# Phase 2-A.2 Step 3: goldens are NOT committed (502 MB+ per suite — see
# docs/PHASE_2A_GPU_RFC.md §3.2.5 sizing rationale). Layout: keep the parent
# tracked, ignore everything inside, then carve back out the per-suite
# manifest files. The unignore order matters — Git does not descend into a
# fully-ignored parent, so the parent + per-suite directories must be
# explicitly unignored before the manifest pattern can take effect.
!/tests/goldens/
/tests/goldens/**
!/tests/goldens/*/
!/tests/goldens/*/manifest.toml
/rust/smooth_core/target/
/rust/smooth_core/Cargo.lock

# Phase 2-A Sub-stage A disposable PoC (lives at ../smooth-spike-poc/, symlinked)
/spike-poc
